From Bill Conner Subject Re Dear Theist Pixie wrote For all the problems technology has caused your types have made things even Must we be reminded of the Inquisition Operation Rescue the Ku Klux Klan Posse Comitatus the Club David Duke Salem Witch Trials the Crusades gay bashings PLUS virtually each and every single war regardless of the level of technology has had theistic organizations cheering on the carnage chaplains and claiming that god was in favor of the whole Don't forget to pray for our troops This is really Every bad thing that's ever happened is because the malefactors were under the influence of religion does anyone really believe I've seen it so often it must be a pretty general opinion in but I want to believe that atheists are really not THAT Please stick to the facts and having accomplished that interpret them Bill